{"tid":610633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛狙擊手屈人手法公開","createTime":"2018-03-30T06:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T06:58:09.000Z","uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"640c4cca0d5070a53462758c72949a20dd236b5b","tid":610633,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"屈所有白票都係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/143933_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F143933_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4916900b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e52f51777ed96105790fa077ab34df9502155a68","tid":610633,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">跟據五毛狙擊手邏輯<br />\n黃之鋒都係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n黃之鋒不滿主流民主派放暗箭　轟口講團結卻向報章吹風匿名批評<br />\n立場報道2018/3/29 &mdash; 15:54<br />\n<br />\nAAA<br />\n黃之鋒、區諾軒<br />\n黃之鋒、區諾軒<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒今天在FB發文，批評主流泛民不時向報章放風，指責自決派和進步民主派等，他指策略檢討批評其無不可，但最低限度應該公開發表，而不是「無成本可言」地躲在匿名批評後。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒在帖文中說：<br />\n<br />\n「沒錯呀，民主派不應分裂，團結仍是非常關鍵，早就成為金科玉律，但講完一套之後，咪實則繼續向報紙放風，正如「主流泛民」周不時透過明報李先知、蘋果西環會客室、信報余錦賢匿名批評激進派呀進步派呀自決派呀（乜都好啦）。<br />\n<br />\n『主流泛民』認識區諾軒比我仲早，佢作為三千票南區票王，有著穩固紮實既地區政績，又點會無跟進政治以外的議題，何來唔係理性務實？投入追殺領展霸權既行動同倡議，更係政圈之中人所皆知，又那裡來的沒有認真議政？<br />\n<br />\n在我而言，策略檢討批評從來並無不可，要質疑要批評咪開誠佈公堅係公開講，問題在於匿名批評根本無成本可言，更某程度上取決於記者同果位政治人物既私交。<br />\n<br />\n口講民主派團結團結團結，就先就要告別依種做壞手勢慣向報紙放風既匿名批評。」"},{"pid":"86ceb68a32d626df445222b35f5bf43d80553a2f","tid":610633,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/144137_25bb1a00d64a617c2b684ed9e55d7b83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F144137_25bb1a00d64a617c2b684ed9e55d7b83.gif&h=b7c15f2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba2b5c07df2f0e8fb3e8dba2f0395984070193e","tid":610633,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fdaeaa274e7424bffc40bebb51848b42f0e30f8","tid":610633,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ea90561a259ac9a832c4ddb824f2439a7bad6f9","tid":610633,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"86ceb68a32d626df445222b35f5bf43d80553a2f","tid":610633,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/144137_25bb1a00d64a617c2b684ed9e55d7b83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F144137_25bb1a00d64a617c2b684ed9e55d7b83.gif&h=b7c15f2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛Ikuchan<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2F&d=yY4n0Etsvt53l5azvnt8ZgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9c7250a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/144410_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F144410_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=30a41757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"08eda2afcfeaac23d29bcd24a89e07bc50c4f9dc","tid":610633,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6fdaeaa274e7424bffc40bebb51848b42f0e30f8","tid":610633,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0